of Columbus.

00:32:04.970 --> 00:32:08.810
There are many talks about
the new world of music,

00:32:08.810 --> 00:32:13.100
a title that gets picked up by
Dvorak later for a work that some

00:32:13.100 --> 00:32:15.330
of you may know, the
New World Symphony.

00:32:15.330 --> 00:32:19.940
And additionally, he
hears that first week

00:32:19.940 --> 00:32:23.760
because his hotel is right over one
of the main parade routes all sort

00:32:23.760 --> 00:32:27.800
of the music of America,
blacksmiths choirs, you know,

00:32:27.800 --> 00:32:30.800
