00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:53.990
And one of the real preoccupations
of Jeanette Thurber was the idea

00:32:53.990 --> 00:32:59.620
that Dvorak should fuse the
local styles of the United States

00:32:59.620 --> 00:33:01.230
to create something Czech.

00:33:01.230 --> 00:33:06.950
And that meant to her mind not only
the various styles of Celtic music

00:33:06.950 --> 00:33:09.500
or French music, but primarily

00:33:09.500 --> 00:33:13.870
in her view African-American
and Native American.

00:33:13.870 --> 00:33:20.230
