who is an extraordinary singer,

00:33:55.320 --> 00:33:58.640
whose grandfather had been a slave.

00:33:58.640 --> 00:34:02.220
And as Burley walked with
his grandfather in Erie,

00:34:02.220 --> 00:34:05.290
