01:00:04.040 --> 01:00:08.080
So, you know, there's just so many
encounters that he might've had

01:00:08.080 --> 01:00:09.380
that we know nothing about.

01:00:09.380 --> 01:00:13.410
The ones we know about primarily
are either his encounters

01:00:13.410 --> 01:00:20.440
