people who don't know each other

01:00:32.770 --> 01:00:34.280
who all seem to say the same thing.

01:00:34.280 --> 01:00:37.720
So the relationship between
Harry Burley and Dvorak

01:00:37.720 --> 01:00:42.340
that one profound way that
that he heard black music.

01:00:42.340 --> 01:00:45.440
He knew this Sissieretta Jones,

01:00:45.440 --> 01:00:49.850
